ecret son, who the latter rapper acknowledged publicly only months earlier. Following the song’s release, Drake reportedly unfollowed The Weeknd, his former protégé, on Instagram, sparking full-on feud rumors. The Weeknd has not commented on “War.” Source: E-news Vanguard News Drake was named the top artist at Sunday’s 2017 Billboard Music Awards, breaking the record for the most awards won in a single year with 13 total wins. May 22, 2017 In "Entertainment" Canadian rapper, Aubrey Graham, popularly called Drake has reportedly bought an iphone cover case made of 18-karat white gold, dotted with blue and white diamonds worth $400,000. February 19, 2019 In "Music" Drake’s “One Dance” featuring Wizkid, has been nominated as one of the Top hot 100 songs for the 2017 Billboard awards scheduled to hold in Las Vegas on May 21. April 10, 2017 In "News"